A_t = \frac{A}{H^2} t^2
 V = \int_0^H A_t dt
 \frac{A_t}{A} = \frac{t^2}{H^2} 
 V = \frac{A}{H^2} \int_0^H t^2 dt = \frac{1}{3} AH. 
